Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Gaia, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Swordsman is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse the Demon's Summon with the Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon, rip Dark Knight Gaia apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi. I finally understand the true fun in Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is a true Duel, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Final Game of Friendship!\N Yugi VS Jounouchi (Part 2)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very superb Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Yugi boy has technique, \Nand Jounouchi boy has power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}But, right now Jounouchi boy's tactics went up, and he's pushed Yugi boy into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}So, Yugi boy, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Yugi's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi won't give up so easily. \NThe battle has just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}\N is feeling the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel will probably get more and more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?\N You want to give up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This turn I'll use this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's Black Magician finally came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't fight against my Black Demon's Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of a strong Attack Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you put it in Attack Mode, it'll become the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I've also said a Duel is a combination of both Monster Cards and Magic Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Silk Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Silk Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi used it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}You finally decided to use \Nyour best techniques, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Which Silk Hat did Black Magician hide in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}I knew he would eventually use them, but...\N this is really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Which Silk Hat\N is the Black Magician hiding in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll blast 'em one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Black Demon's Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you missed him, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only three left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... Which Silk Hat is the Black Magician hiding in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Any one else notice that Jounouchi's been taking more time to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably changing his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this turn, he is probably planning a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you would destroy \Nmy Monsters one by one, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I destroy Black Magician, then you'll have no success later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ending this Duel that quickly would be a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warrior Monster, Garoozis,\N in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Attack is 1800. Black Magician's Attack is 2500.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my turn, I want to give you a step to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to continue fighting with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if destroying Black Magician is easy, it's not fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come attack it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Jounouchi make\N a mistake or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's luring Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} plans to force out Black Magician, who is hiding in the Silk Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Come. It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, I'm sorry, \Nbut I can't accept your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put this card in a\N Silk Hat and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}What did he put under it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}It's impossible to trick him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}You insist on hiding the Black Magician under one of the Magical Silk Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}And he hid another card under it.\N It probably is a Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} probably thinks the card I hid is a Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Will you still have the courage to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Damn it. Even if I keep thinking, I'm not coming up with anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Looks like I'll have to take a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon, battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}This is why the Mind Scan brings me ecstasy. \NI can know exactly what they are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}The problem is the last two Silk Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}No matter who attacks, there will be a significant change in the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such amazing thinking between the two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't think Jounouchi would be able to think about Yugi's play...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It would be impossible \Nif he hadn't progressed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he's now become a great Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's making me nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Silk Hats remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:08:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is Black Magician.\N The other is a set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, the attack will be sure \Nto reach something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Silk Hat has a Trap Card, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack and you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to do just that! \NBut whatever happens, I won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the Duelist I'm fighting with right now isn't any {\i1}normal{\i0} Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon, attack a Silk Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hexagram Curse...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Attack has decreased!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. Just in case, I change Garoozis to Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is my turn, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating Yugi really isn't an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Jounouchi is doing pretty good against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Even if the attack just now didn't work, both their strengths are equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they are both using their most powerful Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi has the advantage, possessing \Nmore regeneration spells, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be useless to try to think too much into a Duel that has reached this much depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}He really isn't letting me win so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Impressive! The Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} in front of me right now isn't scared of his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Furthermore, he's not acting so carelessly any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}This is the capacity of a Duelist, \Nto think calmly and quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you're the ideal opponent for me to go all out with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}This is now becoming a fight of willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}I look forward to the end result of this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}But this is no time to be admiring him.\N It's time to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat this Black Demon's Dragon, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.\N Are you ready, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Secret Arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this Magic Card, I can increase Black Magician's Attack by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Demon's Dragon has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo, Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Yugi... You're strong...\N {\b0}Too{\b1} strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Just as I thought, I can't win against you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, this is the proof of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}We can't worry about the outcome.\N We must fight with all our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}That is our Duel.\N Isn't that right, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, you did great getting this far, but you can't go on anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, we still don't know what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result still hasn't been decide between them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their enthusiasm for the Duel still hasn't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}I've worked hard for this day, but I still can't beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Damn it! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}I wanted to see\N your face one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}That's right... \NShe's still waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Yes... Whatever happens, I must not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}What did he draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle starts now, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Dragon! Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I set this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Could that face-down card be the Time Wizard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}If it is, it will attack as Thousand Dragon instead of the Baby Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Then I must kill it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle! Black Magician, attack Baby Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you proceed!\N I activate a Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garoozis! Chained Boomerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Oh no... Because of Baby Dragon... \NI thought it was the Time Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Yugi boy made an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}He understands his opponent too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}He messed up, even if it's just one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}This is what makes this Duel \Nso complex and interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to put an end to this \Nhas finally arrived, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins, no anger towards him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come such a long way.\N And I think I've gotten pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over 'till I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be at stake on this next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm beaten in this Duel, I still won't regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I drew the best card for our match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? \NDon't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time Magician!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd use this card in our final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right, use this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it'll give you a hand when you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really? Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's helped me out of a ton of pinches before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, without it, \NI wouldn't be Dueling you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Time Magician is the most appropriate card \Nto put an end to our Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this, Yugi!\N This is my best card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magician! Time Roulette!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of Time Magician's influence, Black Magician will age!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,became an old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi won!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}This is unbelievable... \NWill I actually defeat Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}No, this isn't a dream or an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Yugi, don't be mad at me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle! Thousand Nose Breath!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makiu Evil Rain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn... \NHow can the Evil Rain be activated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, because of Time Magician's influence, Baby Dragon wasn't the only Monster affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magician who now received \Na thousand years of life and experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,became a sage mastering all the arcanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Black-Robed Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He enables me to add a Magic Card of my choice from my deck into my hand during each of our turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During your turn, the effect of Makiu \Nwas activated which caused the rain to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, during my turn, I'll be able \Nto add a new Magic Card to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the power of the Great Black-Robed Sage, \NI can now use a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I resurrect The Evil Dragon - \NBlack Demon's Dragon, in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really didn't hold back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is what it means to be a True Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be able to understand now... The meaning of the battle between the two's strong link with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}That was superb. A very good Duel, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\}I will defeat you for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here Yugi, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, the prize money is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to defeat Pegasus and save Grandpa, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the prize money for Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s eyes can be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... Yugi, you have to win... \Nagainst this Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally Yugi and Pegasus' battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus uses the Millennium Eye to look at his opponent's cards, but you can't lose, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Grandpa, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Where's Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...! Where did he go \Nat such an important time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Final Duel! Yugi VS Pegasus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:21:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:22:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
